         <abstract>
            <p>
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
                are instructed to send fees for land-measuring and for rent-free lands from the
               villages of district (pargana)
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
                without delay.</p>
