   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1661_dai_lns235ms_m1_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" xml:id="orig_div1" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:lang="per" type="maintext" xml:id="orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبده الاماثل و الاقران
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                چودری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
                قانونگوی
               <lb/>پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
                بدانند که سلامی از بابت نظر پیمایش تفریق
               <lb/> از هر ده پرگنه مذکور بخواجه
               <persName ref="#jhabarNarayan">
                  <unclear>جهبر</unclear>
                   ناراین</persName>
                واصل نمایند که
               <lb/>بحضور بفرستند دراین باب نهایت تاکید
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="low">داشته</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="high">دانسته</rdg>
               </app>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور عمل نمایند و از نوشته تخلف نورزند
               <lb/>تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  <num>۴</num>
                   ماه جمادی الثانی سنه
                  <num>۱۰۷۱</num>
               </date>
               <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" xml:id="orig_div3" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور مقرر شناسند
               <lb/> نهایت تاکید دانند
               <unclear>آنچه</unclear>
               <app>
                  <rdg cert="low">نکارد ارضه</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="medium">بکار داخله</rdg>
               </app>
               <lb/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                  مرید باخلاص
                  <persName ref="#asadullah">اسد الله</persName>
                  <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازس خانی</persName>
                  <gap/>
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                     <num>۱۰۷۱</num>
                  </date>
               </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1661_dai_lns235ms_m1_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" xml:id="orig_div4" rend="top right">
            <p>
               پروانه وکالت دستگاه میرزا جیو
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <unclear>بار</unclear>
                سلامی بنظر پیمایش</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" xml:id="orig_div5" rend="top right">
            <p>به
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
                چودری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
                قانونگوی پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               <unclear>برسد</unclear>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p><lb/>Eminent among Equals and Contemporaries
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> 
                <lb/>of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, know that the fee for the tribute for the measurement of the divisions for holders of excessive rent free lands 
               <lb/>from each village of the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> should be delivered to Khwaja
               <persName ref="#jhabarNarayan">
                  <unclear>Jhabar</unclear>
                   Narayan</persName>
                [so] that he 
                <lb/>can send it to the Lord. Being extremely diligent in this matter, 
                <lb/>execute as written. And do not cause any delays [in executing that which is] written. 
               <lb/>Written on the
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">4th of the month of Jumada al-sani, year 1071</date>.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p><lb/>Know it to be established as written, [and]
               <lb/>be especially diligent in this matter.
               <lb/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                  <persName ref="#asadullah">Asadullah</persName> special disciple of
                  <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>
                  <gap/>
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1071</date>
               </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of the representative of the court <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_mirza">Mirza</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>;
               <lb rend="empty"/> <unclear>registered</unclear> fee for the tribute of measurement. </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>
               <unclear>Deliver</unclear>
                to
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>.
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
